urlProducto: I was just trying to get the Thank You cards set up so we could have them available for folks to either download or to print when they are needed.  I would love to have them available soon and would also like to add some additional items as well which could be used by sales reps.
How about setting a due time by July 3 to have the Thank You cards ready to roll and then we can look at the brand product guide and the other product postcards we could post to the site.
